title: HOUR 1- Ross Tucker Sep 28, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Ross Tucker Sep 28, 2020
description:
Ross Tucker tells Dan that he was working the Eagles game that ended in a tie and that the fans in Philly are not happy. Ross says fans would rather the Eagles go for the win and lose rather than settle for a tie.
